ìíŸ@271c165445cbc3c8656c1c13b58dddaa51496648e5491dedfc9ccb0ff506de88⁄Title: This week in Nushell #262
Path: Nushell
Content:
fdncred 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13739] removed 
``cfg_atter tarpaulin``
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13710] updated virtual terminal processing
.
ayax79 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13726] added expression support for 
``polars replace``
 and 
``polars replace-all``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13724] expression support for 
``polars uppercase``
 and 
``polars lowercase``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13711] new 
``polars``
 commands for converting string columns to integer and decimal columns
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13707] changed the category for 
``panic``
, adding search terms and examples
.
cptpiepmatz 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13708] switched to 
``heck``
 from 
``convert_case``
 for 
``nu-derive-value``
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13699] added record key renaming for the 
``IntoValue``
 and 
``FromValue``
 derive macros
.
Bahex 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13705] added split cell-path
.
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13698] used the right options in custom completions
.
sholderbach 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13695] simplified the bug reporting form
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13694] removed 
``system-clipboard``
 from the default build
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13693] removed 
``str deunicode``
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13691] set up global 
``cargo``
 lint configuration
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13690] removed an unnecessary sort in the 
``explore``
 search function
.
weirdan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13692] enabled respect for user-defined 
``$env.NU_LOG_FORMAT``
 and 
``$env.NU_LOG_DATE_FORMAT``
.
cyradotpink 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell/pull/13413] fixed parsing of record values containing colons
.
