Path: Documentation
Content:
yo-goto 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1539] fixed the nothing type literal (
``none``
 ‚Üí 
``null``
)
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1538] fixed link parentheses on the Float type page
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1536] fixed content in the binary data type table
.
maniaphobic 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1537] updated string.md
.
ysthakur 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1533] added info on setting XDG_CONFIG_HOME
.
Hofer-Julian 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1531] fixed capitalization for headings levels 2 and 3
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1530] corrected a copy-paste mistake
, 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1529] ensured consistent headline capitalization
, and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1523] fixed a link to handling missing data
.
NotTheDr01ds 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1528] promoted Installation to its own top-level Book chapter
.
weirdan 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1525] replaced 
``it``
 with 
``elt``
, 
``row``
, 
``line``
, etc. (batch 2)
 and 
[link: https://github.com/nushell/nushell.github.io/pull/1524] continued replacing 
``it``
 with 
``elt``
, 
``row``
, 
``line``
, etc.
.
